work.title: Hør, hvor let dens Vinger smækker
Listen, how its pinions scuttle

history.p: According to his diary, Nielsen composed the melody on 23 December 1914. It might originally have been intended for the first volume of En Snes danske Viser (1915, CNW Coll. 9). For some unknown reason, the melody was only later included in the second volume of 1917.
